CustomField.description: The date the Contact starts the Program. If the Program Engagement stage is set to Enrolled or Active, the Start Date is set to TODAY() by the Process Builder process titled Template: Program Engagement Name. To edit the Process Builder process, clone the template and edit it.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The date the Contact starts the Program. If the Program Engagement stage is set to Enrolled or Active, the Start Date is set to TODAY() by the Process Builder process titled Template: Program Engagement Name. Clone the process template to edit it.
CustomField.label: Start Date
